tml" label="Body Copy" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"><![CDATA[<p>Community Members and Personal Employment Postings only, please.</p>
<p><strong>Businesses</strong>, please use <a href="https://byui-csm.symplicity.com/employers/" title="Career Navigator" target="_blank">Career Navigator</a> to hire students.</p>
<p>Use this page to post temporary or short term positions - when you only need a student for a few hours, a few days or a few weeks.</p>
<p>Please complete the following to request a help-wanted posting. Your request will be reviewed and you will be notified when your posting is approved or denied. Requirements can be found on the &nbsp;<a href="x32480.xml" title="Help Wanted">Help Wanted</a> page. If there are special instructions, or information about the posting you'd like to tell us, please include your comments in the "other/comments" box.</p>
<p>If you have questions, please <a href="x24268.xml" title="Contact Us">contact us</a>.</p>
